cdata.name: RoundCoin
cdata.desc: Round is a project for a decentralized eSports gaming platform. The platform allows its participants or a group of participants to compete between each other for money in such popular online games as League of Legends, Dota 2 or Counter-Strike, etc. Based on Ethereum, the platform completely eliminates the dependence on third parties in determining the winner and paying the award in cybersports.  RoundCoin is used to bet on eSports matches.
